Package: TextSentiment
Type: Package
Title: Generates Text Sentiment Score Using Microsoft API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: TextSentiment Team <TextSentiment@TextSentiment.net>
Description: The package calculates sentiment score for text document using Microsoft Cognitive Services API. The package allows batch and individual post requests and also has functions to visualize the sentiment score.    
